<h3 dir="auto" class="">Things I Love</h3>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words"><strong>Starfield</strong>: The 3D star effect (<span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">z</span> depth, perspective scaling) is mesmerizing and lightweightŌĆö1000 stars with minimal lag. ItŌĆÖs a subtle nod to cosmic exploration, fitting ŌĆ£Forbidden Knowledge.ŌĆØ</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>Font Integration</strong>: Loading <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">Sga-Regular</span> via <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">@font-face</span> with fallbacks (woff2, woff, ttf) is robust. The toggle is a delightful Easter egg for SGA fans.</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>OG Meta Tags</strong>: Including <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">og:image</span> with <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">forbidden-knowledge.png</span> ensures a slick preview when sharedŌĆösmart move for visibility.</li>
</ul>
